{"tid":246976,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂喜] 一個月不到，Galaxy S8 銷量已破 500 萬部","createTime":"2017-05-17T12:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T20:14:14.000Z","uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a530ca54998ea095bbd3d601c314234a7495f9e0","tid":246976,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/881bad7c7600f8f972237b79d048a4a1/205275587/mg-1787-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2F881bad7c7600f8f972237b79d048a4a1%2F205275587%2Fmg-1787-1.jpg&h=e0880b97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在預購量告捷之後，不到一個月的時間三星最新旗艦 Galaxy S8 與 S8+ 的銷售量也傳出亮眼成績。據報，該公司在一個月內於全球，已經售出了超過 500 萬部 S8 系列新機。由此看來，在 Note 7 事件的事件之後三星的補救措施的確收到了不錯的成效，依然讓消費者願意相信並給予支持。與前代旗艦 S7 相比，Galaxy S8 的預購量有著 30% 的成長，至於銷售量最終是否也將大幅度超越前代機種，則還有待後續觀察了。<br />\n<br />\n目前而言，除了上季總銷售些微下滑至 5,080 萬台的 iPhone 是長期以來的對手外，同時間點推出的旗艦機還有華為的 P10 Plus、LG G6 等機型，似乎都沒有擋住 S8 的勢頭。不過，接著還有同樣搭載 S835 與 Dual Pixel 對焦系統，而且售價相當誘人的 HTC「擠壓」旗艦 U11即將上市，它是否將會搶走三星的聚光燈也將是個十分值得觀察的重點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b58b5e310b802f3de34a7d476d829fad79118b7","tid":246976,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"有meizu唔買買三星係咩邏輯"},{"pid":"11b09fb02759011812c0baacdc0aab652081446c","tid":246976,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"銀河（蓋樂世）8號和8號加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b2df5025c11a9b2b5906cb4ecfcc3ccf960f65","tid":246976,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"講咩HTC呀 佢出得返M7水準先講啦"},{"pid":"1306e0545ee80d83248f894d4f2a23bd0b68987a","tid":246976,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-